    <h1 headingId="h.dzcjtg8n4khe">
      <t>Boot41 Backend Bootcamp — 2026 Edition</t>
    </h1>
    <p>
      <t>
        <b>Overview:</b>
      </t>
      <t> Evaluation framework, timeline, and project assignments for the 2026 cohort of Backend Engineering Interns.</t>
    </p>
    <p />
    <h2 headingId="h.rpr08dey9k9q">
      <t>Program Structure</t>
    </h2>
    <li parent="kix.s01j59yr8bat">
      <t>Duration: 8 weeks</t>
    </li>
    <li parent="kix.s01j59yr8bat">
      <t>Cohort size: 20 interns</t>
    </li>
    <li parent="kix.s01j59yr8bat">
      <t>Tech stack: FastAPI, SQLAlchemy, Docker, Temporal, Google Cloud</t>
    </li>
    <li parent="kix.s01j59yr8bat" level="1">
      <t>Cloud services: Cloud Run, Cloud Storage, Cloud SQL</t>
    </li>
    <li parent="kix.s01j59yr8bat" level="1">
      <t>Observability: Cloud Logging, Cloud Trace</t>
    </li>
    <li parent="kix.s01j59yr8bat">
      <t>Evaluation: Weekly demos + final presentation</t>
    </li>
    <p />
    <h2 headingId="h.xsabmamnbexi">
      <t>Evaluation Criteria</t>
    </h2>
    <li parent="kix.ir2coed9ss5">
      <t>Correctness — does the system behave as specified?</t>
    </li>
    <li parent="kix.ir2coed9ss5">
      <t>Edge case handling — are all constraints enforced?</t>
    </li>
    <li parent="kix.ir2coed9ss5">
      <t>Code quality — clean, readable, well-structured code</t>
    </li>
    <li parent="kix.ir2coed9ss5">
      <t>API design — RESTful, consistent, well-documented</t>
    </li>
    <li parent="kix.ir2coed9ss5">
      <t>Testing — unit tests and integration tests</t>
    </li>
    <li parent="kix.ir2coed9ss5" />
